description:
My #HoneyDew this week is the one and only, Dr. Drew! Like a lot of you, I’ve been a fan of Dr. Drew for a long time and I’m fired up to have him on The Dew! He opens up about his strained relationship with his parents growing up, his early days at KROQ working around the clock, his prostate cancer & some untold stories from Celebrity Rehab! Subscribe, download & review!
